Pre-Game Insights: Since we do not get enough time in the national team, we must make the best of what we have together.
We’re playing the Intercontinental now, and the Tri-Nation in Vietnam next month, followed by another FIFA window in November, and that’s it.
We must not only be physically strong, but mentally as well. The bond within the team has to be stronger than ever.
The last couple of months have not been easy. We came so close, but yet we could not make it. But it’s quite simple for us. We just have to learn from it all and become better, there’s no other way.
